creator: Abdullah Alawadhi
descriptionHtml:
The main purpose of creating the application is offering Chalets rentals and resorts in Kuwait. The application also has other two categories which are Catering and Shopping and both of these categories are serving the chalets rented through the app. All of these categories are third party suppliers,so the application will be as a platform for the suppliers. The app offers online payments only and transactions history for suppliers and each supplier will have his own dashboard.
The revenue from this app is taking a specific percentage from the all the transactions through the application
